long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Tabby" is a user-friendly Chrome extension designed to streamline tab management and enhance browsing efficiency. 

With Tabby, users can organize their tabs effortlessly by grouping them according to their preferences. 

Whether it's for work, research, or leisure, Tabby allows users to assign custom colors and text labels to different tab groups, enabling easy identification and swift navigation. 

This extension empowers users to create a personalized browsing experience tailored to their needs and workflow. 

Say goodbye to cluttered tabs and hello to a tidy, organized browsing environment with Tabby.
